# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Local development
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Leave VITE_API_URL unset. Vite proxies /api to Express (vite.config.ts → port 3000).
# Run: npm run dev:backend from repo root alongside npm run dev

# VITE_DEV_API_PROXY=http://127.0.0.1:3000

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Production. Choose ONE primary API strategy
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------

# (A) Vercel same origin API (Swap, market, Jupiter, /api/rpc). RECOMMENDED
#     Leave VITE_API_URL unset (or remove it in Vercel). Do NOT set VITE_API_MODE=external.
#     Deploy repo root so `api/` serverless ships; set JUPITER_API_KEY, SOLANA_RPC_URL on Vercel.
#     See docs/DEPLOYMENT.md

# (B) All /api/* on a separate host (VPS Express). Opt in split deploy
# VITE_API_MODE=external
# VITE_API_URL=https://api.example.com

# (C) Hybrid: Vercel SPA + Agent chat on VPS (set ANTHROPIC_API_KEY on the server). Use ONE of:
#     • VITE_AGENT_API_URL=https://your-api-origin.example.com   (browser → VPS /api/agent/chat; set CORS on VPS)
#     • Or omit this and set AGENT_BACKEND_ORIGIN on Vercel (see api/.env.example) to proxy same-origin /api/agent/chat → VPS
# VITE_AGENT_API_URL=
# x402-solana uses same origin `/api/rpc` by default (Vercel). Fallbacks: agent `/api/rpc`, then public Ankr.
# Force agent RPC: VITE_X402_USE_AGENT_RPC=1. Explicit JSON-RPC: VITE_X402_RPC_URL=…
# Ensure VPS CORS_ORIGIN lists your Vercel domain(s) if the browser calls the VPS.

# Optional: browser-direct Solana JSON-RPC (must allow your web origin). Prefer Vercel `SOLANA_RPC_URL` + same-origin `/api/rpc`.
# VITE_SOLANA_RPC_URL=
# VITE_X402_RPC_URL=
# VITE_X402_USE_AGENT_RPC=

# When HTTP RPC is same-origin /api/rpc, subscriptions need a real WSS (Vercel /api has no WS).
# Default in code is mainnet public WSS; override with Helius etc. if you prefer.
# VITE_SOLANA_WS_URL=wss://api.mainnet-beta.solana.com

# --- Planktonomous Autopilot (Polygon): WalletConnect v2 ---
# Create a project at https://cloud.reown.com (WalletConnect Cloud) and paste the Project ID.
# Optional: without it, MetaMask (injected) + Coinbase Wallet still work.
# VITE_WALLETCONNECT_PROJECT_ID=

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Privy (https://www.privy.io/) — optional; enables Sign in + embedded wallets in the header
# Full guide: docs/privy-integration.md (server secrets stay in Vercel / api env — never VITE_*)
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# VITE_PRIVY_APP_ID=
# Optional app client from Dashboard → App clients
# VITE_PRIVY_CLIENT_ID=
